gy, NTPC, and GSFC anchor the ecosystem, spanning infrastructure, production, and end-use, with gradual progress expected.","summary":"India's green hydrogen push targets 5 MMT by 2030, leveraging Rs 8T investments via National Green Hydrogen Mission with policy support and incentives.\nStocks like L&T, Indian Oil, JSW Energy, NTPC, and GSFC anchor the ecosystem, spanning infrastructure, production, and end-use, with gradual progress expected.","url":"https://www.financialexpress.com/market/stock-insights/the-rs-8-trillion-pivot-5-infrastructure-stocks-anchoring-indias-green-hydrogen-supply-chain/4142239/","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-13T05:30:00","source":"Financial Express"},{"id":"260211151716257","title":"GSFC's quality grade downgraded to Average, Mojo Score now at 40.\nSell rating reflects concerns on returns, growth, and capital efficiency.","summary":"GSFC's quality grade downgraded to Average, Mojo Score now at 40.\nSell rating reflects concerns on returns, growth, and capital efficiency.","url":"https://www.marketsmojo.com/news/stocks-in-action/gujarat-state-fertilizers-chemicals-ltd-quality-grade-downgrade-highlights-mixed-business-fundamentals-3832143","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-11T08:00:13","source":"Marketsmojo"},{"id":"483979","title":"GSFC announced audio recording link of investor call on Q3 FY25 results.\nThe recording is available on GSFC's website for stakeholder reference.","summary":"GSFC announced audio recording link of investor call on Q3 FY25 results.\nThe recording is available on GSFC's website for stakeholder reference.","url":"https://www.bseindia.com/stockinfo/AnnPdfOpen.aspx?Pname=fa0f98ff-4601-4066-8fd0-e3b987289b22.pdf","imageUrl":null,"pubDate":"2026-02-10T19:12:53","source":"BSE"},{"id":"808971019839322368","title":"GSFC reported strong Q3 performance in revenue, profit, and margins.","summary":"GSFC reported strong Q3 performance in revenue, profit, and margins.","url":"https://sqst.in/0PBta","imageUrl":null,"pubDat